source.name: Uniform Soybean Tests, Southern States
source.description: The Uniform Soybean Tests, Southern States is an on-going standardized soybean testing program originating in 1943 and covers the Southern States region of the US. The annual reports have been scanned into a secured pdf format and placed online.
